ygData.messageBody:
Hi everyone,

I just bought a new DELL computer for gaming. When I played EQ the
other day, I went to the OVERTHERE. Instead of seeing the usual
creatures (succulents, rhinos, Sarnaks and tigers), I see only
various sizes of human men. Now this computer is supposed to have a
top line graphic card, so I'm not sure how to adjust my settings to
see the normal bestiary for this area. Does anyone know what I
should adjust to get things back to normal?

Thanks....
